1
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:52,736
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,736 --> 00:00:56,434
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:02,439 --> 00:01:03,240
Boyfriend?

4
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:14,400
Yes. Xiao Jin is Ji Xuan's boyfriend.

5
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,719
Deputy GM of Rongsheng Group.

6
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,159
He's Ji Xuan's first love.

7
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,159
Got it.

8
00:01:19,439 --> 00:01:21,879
Song, who is Ji Xuan?

9
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,599
Why do you care about her?

10
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,439
Rongsheng ball invitation.

11
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,319
Song.

12
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:30,000
As your buddy, I have to warn you.

13
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:33,200
Being the other man has no future.

14
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,239
(Gala Ball Invitation)

15
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:35,359
You talk too much.

16
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,480
No future.

17
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,840
Mr. Wang, long time no see.

18
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,599
Long time no see.

19
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,159
Okay.

20
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:49,920
It's been ages.

21
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,519
Yeah.

22
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:52,840
Thank you for your help.

23
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,560
You're welcome.

24
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,400
Happy to help out.

25
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,439
Just a little help.

26
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,560
You really helped us a lot.

27
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,840
My pleasure.

28
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:02,840
Mr. Li.

29
00:02:02,976 --> 00:02:03,640
Hello.

30
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:09,599
You look pretty.

31
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,680
What's wrong?

32
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,800
Is work too exhausting lately?

33
00:02:40,352 --> 00:02:40,960
Watch out.

34
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:59,240
Mr. Song, your presence here

35
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,840
brings great honor to us.

36
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,039
Mr. Wang, I'm flattered.

37
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,919
Miss Ji, we meet again.

38
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,759
Mr. Song, I'm Xiao Jin, Xuan's fiancé,

39
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,879
deputy GM of Rongsheng Group.

40
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:23,159
Miss Ji, I didn't bring
a dance partner today.

41
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,680
May I have this dance?

42
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,599
Sorry, Mr. Song.

43
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,159
I'm a bit tired today.

44
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:41,199
Is this how you treat your clients?

45
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:54,319
It's an honor for her to dance with you.

46
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,319
You're very capable at work,

47
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:21,319
but your taste
in boyfriends isn't great.

48
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,079
No need for your concern.

49
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,920
I prefer the way you were last night.

50
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:39,319
Now, you understand
why I gave you the dress?

51
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:57,600
If your boyfriend knew

52
00:04:57,959 --> 00:05:00,560
you wore the dress
I gave you to the ball with him,

53
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:03,000
would he feel a bit guilty toward me?

54
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:07,199
Mr. Song, it was an accident last night.

55
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,560
Miss Ji, relax.

56
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,959
I won't cling to you
just because of that.

57
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,120
But I did help you.

58
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,639
How will you repay me?

59
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,079
I'll buy you dinner.

60
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,759
You know,

61
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:29,600
Mr. Song and Miss Ji
look quite compatible.

62
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:33,040
Don't you think, Xiao Jin?

63
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:38,360
Her future husband
is standing right here.

64
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:42,319
Besides, Mr. Song is already engaged.

65
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:44,480
Xiao Jin.

66
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,959
Don't get jealous.

67
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,399
No, no.

68
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,319
Xuan, what did Mr. Song say to you?

69
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,279
Business.

70
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,839
Are you two close?

71
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,120
He's my client.

72
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,800
Could you

73
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,639
introduce me to him?

74
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,920
I don't want to. You go yourself.

75
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,720
Help me out.
He doesn't seem easy to approach.

76
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:32,639
Let's go.

77
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:36,160
Mr. Song.

78
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,360
I'm Xiao Jin, deputy GM
of Rongsheng Group.

79
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:41,120
Didn't you just introduce yourself?

80
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,839
Mr. Song.

81
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:46,639
Xiao Jin is young and capable,
my right-hand man.

82
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,120
I'm getting older,

83
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,439
struggling with many things.

84
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:54,360
I'd appreciate
any support you can offer him.

85
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,240
I told you.

86
00:06:57,560 --> 00:07:01,360
Introducing yourself
isn't just about title and name.

87
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,399
- Yeah.
- You need a highlight.

88
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:06,480
For example, you could tell Mr. Song

89
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,480
you and Miss Ji
are getting married next month.

90
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:11,488
You can invite him to your wedding.

91
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,399
You're getting married next month?

92
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,160
Yes, Mr. Song.

93
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:18,040
We'll send you an invitation
once we book the venue.

94
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,720
While we're at it,

95
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:24,879
how about

96
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,680
you two have a cross-arm toast?

97
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,639
I'm driving tonight. I can't drink.

98
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,000
Why not let Mr. Song drink for Xiao Jin?

99
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:43,240
Seeing how well you two danced,

100
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:46,439
anyone would think you two are a couple.

101
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:50,839
Xiao Jin and Miss Ji
have plenty of time later.

102
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:51,800
Right?

103
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,439
I'll share in your happiness.

104
00:08:05,312 --> 00:08:05,920
Please.

105
00:08:31,424 --> 00:08:33,759
Isn't Mr. Song already engaged?

106
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,519
Why are they drinking with arms linked?

107
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,039
You know her?

108
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,879
Who knows?

109
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,840
They're so intimate.

110
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,399
If Xiao Jin finds out about last night,

111
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:55,296
do you really think
your wedding will still happen?

112
00:09:07,456 --> 00:09:10,752
(Mrs. Ji, my work situation changed.
The wedding needs to be postponed.)

113
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:13,200
Here's the text message
I drafted for you.

114
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,519
Forward it to my mom.

115
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:17,679
Tell her the wedding needs
to be postponed due to your work change.

116
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:20,440
Later, I'll tell her
about calling off the engagement.

117
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:21,919
Let her be mentally prepared.

118
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,799
Xuan, why call off the engagement
when everything's fine?

119
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,120
Xiao Jin, stop pretending.

120
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:30,639
I saw you with Mrs. Wang last night.

121
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,759
Didn't you also get caught in
a scandal with another man?

122
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,759
Alright, Xuan.

123
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:40,480
I won't ask who the man was last night,

124
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,600
and you don't ask me.

125
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,480
Once we're married,

126
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,279
we can pay off
your dad's debts together.

127
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:47,159
Don't you have any idea

128
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,440
of the scandal's reason?

129
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,639
Shut your mouth,

130
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:52,120
or Mr. Wang will find out
about you and Mrs. Wang immediately.

131
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,559
Ji Xuan, we've been
together for so long.

132
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,960
You sure you want to do that to me?

133
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,759
You do it but fear me talking about it?

134
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:06,879
Mr. Song.

135
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:11,080
I suddenly remembered there is
a project I need to discuss with you.

136
00:10:12,039 --> 00:10:13,720
Hope I'm not interrupting
your alone time?

137
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,120
No, not at all.

138
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:20,159
Mr. Song, I believe Wansheng
is on a par with Rongsheng.

139
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,600
How about we discuss it together?

140
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:23,799
Sure.

141
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:26,480
How about a little competition?

142
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:29,080
Alright, compete in what?

143
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,519
In

144
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,559
shallowness.

145
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,799
In shooting arrows.

146
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:44,600
Fine by me.

147
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:58,000
Mr. Song, you're amazing!

148
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,000
Mr. Song.

149
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:02,600
Since it's leisure time,
how about settling it in a fun way?

150
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:05,879
Ten arrows each.
Whoever wins gets the project.

151
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:09,840
No problem.

152
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,200
Archery is like life.

153
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
You need vision and skill.

154
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:20,279
Most importantly, once the arrow
leaves the bow, there's no turning back.

155
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,279
Think carefully
before making a decision.

156
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:03,000
Xuan, how about
letting me have this deal?

157
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:06,200
After all, isn't my money our money?

158
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:08,240
You're you, and I'm me.

159
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,799
From now on, there is no "us".

160
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:13,240
But you don't know how to shoot arrows.

161
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,720
You'll lose anyway.

162
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,679
Why waste Mr. Song's time?

163
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:23,679
What's wrong?

164
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:26,639
Mr. Song, no need to compete.

165
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:28,000
Xuan doesn't know about archery.

166
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,480
If she doesn't, I can teach her.

167
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,759
I'll teach you.

168
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,759
Wrong posture can easily lead to injury.

169
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:53,120
What's on your mind?

170
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,720
I meant about archery.

171
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:59,200
This is your match against your fiancé.

172
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,799
Focus.

173
00:13:01,279 --> 00:13:03,759
(It's better if he's mistaken.
He'll leave me alone.)

174
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,679
Straighten your back.

175
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,039
Mr. Song, that project...

176
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:19,039
Since you're injured,

177
00:13:19,519 --> 00:13:21,519
let Wansheng Group
handle the resort project.

178
00:13:22,279 --> 00:13:24,759
I'll give Miss Ji a higher commission.

179
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:26,120
Mr. Song, wait, wait!

180
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,120
Mr. Song, I'm fine.

181
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,279
I'm fine, I really am.

182
00:13:28,279 --> 00:13:29,720
I can still keep my balance, I...

183
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,759
- I can still work.
- Take him away.

184
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:33,200
Give me that project. I can...

185
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:34,799
Mr. Song!

186
00:13:36,919 --> 00:13:37,799
Mr. Song!

187
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,960
Mr. Song, I'll work hard.

188
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:41,960
See you.

189
00:13:52,759 --> 00:13:54,559
Follow the game rules.

190
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,639
We agreed on ten arrows.

191
00:13:57,240 --> 00:14:02,840
♪If you ask me just
to stay with you a while♪

192
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:10,200
♪Nothing more, nothing less,
just like this♪

193
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,120
Push the bow forward.

194
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,320
Draw the bow.

195
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:15,360
Three, two...

196
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:16,840
Shoot.

197
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:21,880
♪I am safe, I am sound♪

198
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:25,360
♪Inside your arms♪

199
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:32,000
♪Turn around, turn around♪

200
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:36,279
Come on, shoot again.

201
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,240
Three, two, one, go.

202
00:14:55,124 --> 00:14:56,916
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

203
00:14:57,076 --> 00:14:58,956
♪Flickering neon lights♪

204
00:14:59,156 --> 00:15:02,484
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

205
00:15:02,996 --> 00:15:05,268
♪Every star is♪

206
00:15:05,556 --> 00:15:09,428
♪My heartbeat for you♪

207
00:15:10,740 --> 00:15:12,564
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

208
00:15:12,724 --> 00:15:14,276
♪And land in your arms♪

209
00:15:14,676 --> 00:15:18,132
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

210
00:15:18,388 --> 00:15:20,948
♪In the blue sky♪

211
00:15:21,012 --> 00:15:25,140
♪Your smile still lingers♪

212
00:15:26,068 --> 00:15:29,716
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

213
00:15:29,972 --> 00:15:33,636
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

214
00:15:33,844 --> 00:15:36,756
♪Can't find a cure♪

215
00:15:36,756 --> 00:15:41,268
♪To love you after we've parted♪

216
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:45,492
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

217
00:15:45,492 --> 00:15:49,024
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

218
00:15:49,248 --> 00:15:51,156
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

219
00:15:51,252 --> 00:15:56,404
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

220
00:15:57,044 --> 00:16:00,756
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

221
00:16:00,948 --> 00:16:03,700
♪Can't find a cure♪

222
00:16:03,828 --> 00:16:08,468
♪To love you after we've parted♪

223
00:16:08,636 --> 00:16:12,404
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

224
00:16:12,628 --> 00:16:16,212
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

225
00:16:16,436 --> 00:16:18,336
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

226
00:16:18,336 --> 00:16:23,476
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
